{"tid":459203,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩睇完愛的曝光 好震撼","createTime":"2017-11-05T14:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T12:05:12.000Z","uid":12152,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c79e85fe0b94dea795656d04404faca50d242c48","tid":459203,"uid":12152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://jfdb.jp/data/photo/movie/e4/e4/63/a0/ae9ec59c2447936d3301b622dd5b9a9c_640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjfdb.jp%2Fdata%2Fphoto%2Fmovie%2Fe4%2Fe4%2F63%2Fa0%2Fae9ec59c2447936d3301b622dd5b9a9c_640.jpg&h=235079a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛的曝光係一套由園子溫導演 西島隆弘 満島光主演，片長四小時的電影。<br />\n故名思義佢係一部愛情電影<br />\n係觀看時，我感受到電影分分秒秒都充滿住愛，而且係超越生死既愛，五個主要角色所表達愛既演出，完全打破左我對愛情片既定義。初頭見4小時咁長都好卻步，點知一晚就睇完 冇咩冷場。<br />\n雖然Old news is so......不過都推介比d鐘意愛情故事既巴絲打知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本電影仲有咩經典好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a044091fa65a9369f4d5322e439e730c11887d","tid":459203,"uid":5426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:58:58.000Z","msg":"睇埋園子溫其他作品未？<br />\n<br />\n奇異人生馬戲團<br />\n冷血金魚佬<br />\n自殺俱樂部<br />\n<br />\n夠膽就睇埋 <br />\n一代電影粉皮"},{"pid":"d093144c23774a539547e77ba8c1656fd54725db","tid":459203,"uid":122102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"剪jj <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10461cc13fe54be0c2b9af2d593160bc8d0f56d","tid":459203,"uid":12152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇埋園子溫其他作品未？<br />\n<br />\n奇異人生馬戲團<br />\n冷血金魚佬<br />\n自殺俱樂部<br />\n<br />\n夠膽就睇埋 <br />\n一代電影粉皮</blockquote><br />\n只係睇左庸才 染谷將太好好睇<br />\n一直諗住睇冰冷熱帶魚 但網上搵唔到 可能要買碟<br />\n園子溫太血腥太驚嚇果d唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   多謝推介"},{"pid":"de8022ffaa3ad023701a3a3448c17f7aa59de79d","tid":459203,"uid":12152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剪jj <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJJ 好重戲分 係種愛的象徵"},{"pid":"804ac888ef946a159c4f6920cde756b7801856d5","tid":459203,"uid":12152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042eadab5db09160e671b32977e506618c5fc240","tid":459203,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T09:19:30.000Z","msg":"終於有post講園子溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗上面提過果堆，紀子的餐桌、戀之罪、屍奔女子高校、不是色情電影，呢幾套園子溫嘅作品都可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4360840b191cbbdd660ab01449fe5bd084b6b86c","tid":459203,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:09:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得愛之剝脫最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226c55a4af6487fcdc627f54d7f6cda7b690f60d","tid":459203,"uid":5426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於有post講園子溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗上面提過果堆，紀子的餐桌、戀之罪、屍奔女子高校、不是色情電影，呢幾套園子溫嘅作品都可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜近年回曬塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e848846b15f2d441f1731ba5a24059dd17cc8cd","tid":459203,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>終於有post講園子溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗上面提過果堆，紀子的餐桌、戀之罪、屍奔女子高校、不是色情電影，呢幾套園子溫嘅作品都可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜近年回曬塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但其實又唔係真係講到差咗好多嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係近年佢試多咗唔同風格又拍下商業野咁。<br />\n我上面講果套不是色情電影都係上年先拍嘅，都有番早幾年d風格。話時話一代電影粉皮原來都只係4年前，呢套真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c339dd00af3a778fd7cf2898c8972fe776cb1f","tid":459203,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"本身想睇<br />\n但見到你話C JJ<br />\n都係算了"}]}